literally today, June 14, 2026.

42
00:02:07,940 --> 00:02:08,380
Brand new.

43
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:08,840
Brand new.

44
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:13,960
It's by an independent researcher operating under the name Flyxion, and it is titled Paper

45
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:19,540
Bot Parliament, a multi-agent framework for distinction-centered document analysis.

46
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:20,340
Quite a title.

47
